                            <comment id="42563" author="jay" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 16:32:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch is at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/3511&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/3511&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42562" author="jay" created="Wed, 1 Aug 2012 16:07:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The MGS lost response so OST failed to update the nidtbl version. This is why the nidtbl version matched.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m going to check the nidtbl version # on the client side only to make sure the client is not notified for the restart of OST.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
